				jQuery(this)[ state ? "show" : "hide" ]();
			});

		} else {
			this.animate(genFx("toggle", 3), fn, fn2);
		}

		return this;
	},

	fadeTo: function( speed, to, callback ) {
		return this.filter(":hidden").css("opacity", 0).show().end()
					.animate({opacity: to}, speed, callback);
	},

	animate: function( prop, speed, easing, callback ) {
		var optall = jQuery.speed(speed, easing, callback);

		if ( jQuery.isEmptyObject( prop ) ) {
			return this.each( optall.complete );
		}

		return this[ optall.queue === false ? "each" : "queue" ](function() {
			var opt = jQuery.extend({}, optall), p,
				hidden = this.nodeType === 1 && jQuery(this).is(":hidden"),
				self = this;

			for ( p in prop ) {
				var name = p.replace(rdashAlpha, fcamelCase);

				if ( p !== name ) {
					prop[ name ] = prop[ p ];
					delete prop[ p ];
					p = name;
				}

				if ( prop[p] === "hide" && hidden || prop[p] === "show" && !hidden ) {
					return opt.complete.call(this);
				}

				if ( ( p === "height" || p === "width" ) && this.style ) {
					// Store display property
					opt.display = jQuery.css(this, "display");

					// Make sure that nothing sneaks out
					opt.overflow = this.style.overflow;
				}

				if ( jQuery.isArray( prop[p] ) ) {
					// Create (if needed) and add to specialEasing
					(opt.specialEasing = opt.specialEasing || {})[p] = prop[p][1];
					prop[p] = prop[p][0];
				}
			}

			if ( opt.overflow != null ) {
				this.style.overflow = "hidden";
			}

			opt.curAnim = jQuery.extend({}, prop);

			jQuery.each( prop, function( name, val ) {
				var e = new jQuery.fx( self, opt, name );

				if ( rfxtypes.test(val) ) {
					e[ val === "toggle" ? hidden ? "show" : "hide" : val ]( prop );

				} else {
					var parts = rfxnum.exec(val),
						start = e.cur(true) || 0;

					if ( parts ) {
						var end = parseFloat( parts[2] ),
							unit = parts[3] || "px";

						// We need to compute starting value
						if ( unit !== "px" ) {
							self.style[ name ] = (end || 1) + unit;
							start = ((end || 1) / e.cur(true)) * start;
							self.style[ name ] = start + unit;
						}

						// If a +=/-= token was provided, we're doing a relative animation
						if ( parts[1] ) {
							end = ((parts[1] === "-=" ? -1 : 1) * end) + start;
						}

						e.custom( start, end, unit );

					} else {
						e.custom( start, val, "" );
					}
				}
			});

			// For JS strict compliance
			return true;
		});
	},

	stop: function( clearQueue, gotoEnd ) {
		var timers = jQuery.timers;

		if ( clearQueue ) {
			this.queue([]);
		}

		this.each(function() {
			// go in reverse order so anything added to the queue during the loop is ignored
			for ( var i = timers.length - 1; i >= 0; i-- ) {
				if ( timers[i].elem === this ) {
					if (gotoEnd) {
						// force the next step to be the last
						timers[i](true);
					}

					timers.splice(i, 1);
				}
			}
		});

		// start the next in the queue if the last step wasn't forced
		if ( !gotoEnd ) {
			this.dequeue();
		}

		return this;
	}

});

// Generate shortcuts for custom animations
jQuery.each({
	slideDown: genFx("show", 1),
	slideUp: genFx("hide", 1),
	slideToggle: genFx("toggle", 1),
	fadeIn: { opacity: "show" },
	fadeOut: { opacity: "hide" }
}, function( name, props ) {
	jQuery.fn[ name ] = function( speed, callback ) {
		return this.animate( props, speed, callback );
	};
});

jQuery.extend({
	speed: function( speed, easing, fn ) {
		var opt = speed && typeof speed === "object" ? speed : {
			complete: fn || !fn && easing ||
				jQuery.isFunction( speed ) && speed,
			duration: speed,
			easing: fn && easing || easing && !jQuery.isFunction(easing) && easing
		};

		opt.duration = jQuery.fx.off ? 0 : typeof opt.duration === "number" ? opt.duration :
			jQuery.fx.speeds[opt.duration] || jQuery.fx.speeds._default;

		// Queueing
		opt.old = opt.complete;
		opt.complete = function() {
			if ( opt.queue !== false ) {
				jQuery(this).dequeue();
			}
			if ( jQuery.isFunction( opt.old ) ) {
				opt.old.call( this );
			}
		};

		return opt;
	},

	easing: {
		linear: function( p, n, firstNum, diff ) {
			return firstNum + diff * p;
		},
		swing: function( p, n, firstNum, diff ) {
			return ((-Math.cos(p*Math.PI)/2) + 0.5) * diff + firstNum;
		}
	},

	timers: [],

	fx: function( elem, options, prop ) {
		this.options = options;
		this.elem = elem;
		this.prop = prop;

		if ( !options.orig ) {
			options.orig = {};
		}
	}

});

jQuery.fx.prototype = {
	// Simple function for setting a style value
	update: function() {
		if ( this.options.step ) {
			this.options.step.call( this.elem, this.now, this );
		}

		(jQuery.fx.step[this.prop] || jQuery.fx.step._default)( this );

		// Set display property to block for height/width animations
		if ( ( this.prop === "height" || this.prop === "width" ) && this.elem.style ) {
			this.elem.style.display = "block";
		}
	},

	// Get the current size
	cur: function( force ) {
		if ( this.elem[this.prop] != null && (!this.elem.style || this.elem.style[this.prop] == null) ) {
			return this.elem[ this.prop ];
		}

		var r = parseFloat(jQuery.css(this.elem, this.prop, force));
		return r && r > -10000 ? r : parseFloat(jQuery.curCSS(this.elem, this.prop)) || 0;
	},

	// Start an animation from one number to another
	custom: function( from, to, unit ) {
		this.startTime = now();
		this.start = from;
		this.end = to;
		this.unit = unit || this.unit || "px";
		this.now = this.start;
		this.pos = this.state = 0;

		var self = this;
		function t( gotoEnd ) {
			return self.step(gotoEnd);
		}

		t.elem = this.elem;

		if ( t() && jQuery.timers.push(t) && !timerId ) {
			timerId = setInterval(jQuery.fx.tick, 13);
		}
	},

	// Simple 'show' function
	show: function() {
		// Remember where we started, so that we can go back to it later
		this.options.orig[this.prop] = jQuery.style( this.elem, this.prop );
		this.options.show = true;

		// Begin the animation
		// Make sure that we start at a small width/height to avoid any
		// flash of content
		this.custom(this.prop === "width" || this.prop === "height" ? 1 : 0, this.cur());

		// Start by showing the element
		jQuery( this.elem ).show();
	},

	// Simple 'hide' function
	hide: function() {
		// Remember where we started, so that we can go back to it later
		this.options.orig[this.prop] = jQuery.style( this.elem, this.prop );
		this.options.hide = true;

		// Begin the animation
		this.custom(this.cur(), 0);
	},

	// Each step of an animation
	step: function( gotoEnd ) {
		var t = now(), done = true;

		if ( gotoEnd || t >= this.options.duration + this.startTime ) {
			this.now = this.end;
			this.pos = this.state = 1;
			this.update();

			this.options.curAnim[ this.prop ] = true;

			for ( var i in this.options.curAnim ) {
				if ( this.options.curAnim[i] !== true ) {
					done = false;
				}
			}

			if ( done ) {
				if ( this.options.display != null ) {
					// Reset the overflow
					this.elem.style.overflow = this.options.overflow;

					// Reset the display
					var old = jQuery.data(this.elem, "olddisplay");
					this.elem.style.display = old ? old : this.options.display;

					if ( jQuery.css(this.elem, "display") === "none" ) {
						this.elem.style.display = "block";
					}
				}

				// Hide the element if the "hide" operation was done
				if ( this.options.hide ) {
					jQuery(this.elem).hide();
				}

				// Reset the properties, if the item has been hidden or shown
				if ( this.options.hide || this.options.show ) {
					for ( var p in this.options.curAnim ) {
						jQuery.style(this.elem, p, this.options.orig[p]);
					}
				}

				// Execute the complete function
				this.options.complete.call( this.elem );
			}

			return false;

		} else {
			var n = t - this.startTime;
			this.state = n / this.options.duration;

			// Perform the easing function, defaults to swing
			var specialEasing = this.options.specialEasing && this.options.specialEasing[this.prop];
			var defaultEasing = this.options.easing || (jQuery.easing.swing ? "swing" : "linear");
			this.pos = jQuery.easing[specialEasing || defaultEasing](this.state, n, 0, 1, this.options.duration);
			this.now = this.start + ((this.end - this.start) * this.pos);

			// Perform the next step of the animation
			this.update();
		}

		return true;
	}
};

jQuery.extend( jQuery.fx, {
	tick: function() {
		var timers = jQuery.timers;

		for ( var i = 0; i < timers.length; i++ ) {
			if ( !timers[i]() ) {
				timers.splice(i--, 1);
			}
		}

		if ( !timers.length ) {
			jQuery.fx.stop();
		}
	},
		
	stop: function() {
		clearInterval( timerId );
		timerId = null;
	},
	
	speeds: {
		slow: 600,
 		fast: 200,
 		// Default speed
 		_default: 400
	},

	step: {
		opacity: function( fx ) {
			jQuery.style(fx.elem, "opacity", fx.now);
		},

		_default: function( fx ) {
			if ( fx.elem.style && fx.elem.style[ fx.prop ] != null ) {
				fx.elem.style[ fx.prop ] = (fx.prop === "width" || fx.prop === "height" ? Math.max(0, fx.now) : fx.now) + fx.unit;
			} else {
				fx.elem[ fx.prop ] = fx.now;
			}
		}
	}
});

if ( jQuery.expr && jQuery.expr.filters ) {
	jQuery.expr.filters.animated = function( elem ) {
		return jQuery.grep(jQuery.timers, function( fn ) {
			return elem === fn.elem;
		}).length;
	};
}

function genFx( type, num ) {
	var obj = {};

	jQuery.each( fxAttrs.concat.apply([], fxAttrs.slice(0,num)), function() {
		obj[ this ] = type;
	});

	return obj;
}
if ( "getBoundingClientRect" in document.documentElement ) {
	jQuery.fn.offset = function( options ) {
		var elem = this[0];

		if ( options ) { 
			return this.each(function( i ) {
				jQuery.offset.setOffset( this, options, i );
			});
		}

		if ( !elem || !elem.ownerDocument ) {
			return null;
		}

		if ( elem === elem.ownerDocument.body ) {
			return jQuery.offset.bodyOffset( elem );
		}

		var box = elem.getBoundingClientRect(), doc = elem.ownerDocument, body = doc.body, docElem = doc.documentElement,
			clientTop = docElem.clientTop || body.clientTop || 0, clientLeft = docElem.clientLeft || body.clientLeft || 0,
			top  = box.top  + (self.pageYOffset || jQuery.support.boxModel && docElem.scrollTop  || body.scrollTop ) - clientTop,
			left = box.left + (self.pageXOffset || jQuery.support.boxModel && docElem.scrollLeft || body.scrollLeft) - clientLeft;

		return { top: top, left: left };
	};

} else {
	jQuery.fn.offset = function( options ) {
		var elem = this[0];

		if ( options ) { 
			return this.each(function( i ) {
				jQuery.offset.setOffset( this, options, i );
			});
		}

		if ( !elem || !elem.ownerDocument ) {
			return null;
		}

		if ( elem === elem.ownerDocument.body ) {
			return jQuery.offset.bodyOffset( elem );
		}

		jQuery.offset.initialize();

		var offsetParent = elem.offsetParent, prevOffsetParent = elem,
			doc = elem.ownerDocument, computedStyle, docElem = doc.documentElement,
			body = doc.body, defaultView = doc.defaultView,
			prevComputedStyle = defaultView ? defaultView.getComputedStyle( elem, null ) : elem.currentStyle,
			top = elem.offsetTop, left = elem.offsetLeft;

		while ( (elem = elem.parentNode) && elem !== body && elem !== docElem ) {
			if ( jQuery.offset.supportsFixedPosition && prevComputedStyle.position === "fixed" ) {
				break;
			}

			computedStyle = defaultView ? defaultView.getComputedStyle(elem, null) : elem.currentStyle;
			top  -= elem.scrollTop;
			left -= elem.scrollLeft;

			if ( elem === offsetParent ) {
				top  += elem.offsetTop;
				left += elem.offsetLeft;

				if ( jQuery.offset.doesNotAddBorder && !(jQuery.offset.doesAddBorderForTableAndCells && /^t(able|d|h)$/i.test(elem.nodeName)) ) {
					top  += parseFloat( computedStyle.borderTopWidth  ) || 0;
					left += parseFloat( computedStyle.borderLeftWidth ) || 0;
				}

				prevOffsetParent = offsetParent, offsetParent = elem.offsetParent;
			}

			if ( jQuery.offset.subtractsBorderForOverflowNotVisible && computedStyle.overflow !== "visible" ) {
				top  += parseFloat( computedStyle.borderTopWidth  ) || 0;
				left += parseFloat( computedStyle.borderLeftWidth ) || 0;
			}

			prevComputedStyle = computedStyle;
		}

		if ( prevComputedStyle.position === "relative" || prevComputedStyle.position === "static" ) {
			top  += body.offsetTop;
			left += body.offsetLeft;
		}

		if ( jQuery.offset.supportsFixedPosition && prevComputedStyle.position === "fixed" ) {
			top  += Math.max( docElem.scrollTop, body.scrollTop );
			left += Math.max( docElem.scrollLeft, body.scrollLeft );
		}

		return { top: top, left: left };
	};
}

jQuery.offset = {
	initialize: function() {
		var body = document.body, container = document.createElement("div"), innerDiv, checkDiv, table, td, bodyMarginTop = parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(body, "marginTop", true) ) || 0,
			html = "<div style='position:absolute;top:0;left:0;margin:0;border:5px solid #000;padding:0;width:1px;height:1px;'><div></div></div><table style='position:absolute;top:0;left:0;margin:0;border:5px solid #000;padding:0;width:1px;height:1px;' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'><tr><td></td></tr></table>";

		jQuery.extend( container.style, { position: "absolute", top: 0, left: 0, margin: 0, border: 0, width: "1px", height: "1px", visibility: "hidden" } );

		container.innerHTML = html;
		body.insertBefore( container, body.firstChild );
		innerDiv = container.firstChild;
		checkDiv = innerDiv.firstChild;
		td = innerDiv.nextSibling.firstChild.firstChild;

		this.doesNotAddBorder = (checkDiv.offsetTop !== 5);
		this.doesAddBorderForTableAndCells = (td.offsetTop === 5);

		checkDiv.style.position = "fixed", checkDiv.style.top = "20px";
		// safari subtracts parent border width here which is 5px
		this.supportsFixedPosition = (checkDiv.offsetTop === 20 || checkDiv.offsetTop === 15);
		checkDiv.style.position = checkDiv.style.top = "";

		innerDiv.style.overflow = "hidden", innerDiv.style.position = "relative";
		this.subtractsBorderForOverflowNotVisible = (checkDiv.offsetTop === -5);

		this.doesNotIncludeMarginInBodyOffset = (body.offsetTop !== bodyMarginTop);

		body.removeChild( container );
		body = container = innerDiv = checkDiv = table = td = null;
		jQuery.offset.initialize = jQuery.noop;
	},

	bodyOffset: function( body ) {
		var top = body.offsetTop, left = body.offsetLeft;

		jQuery.offset.initialize();

		if ( jQuery.offset.doesNotIncludeMarginInBodyOffset ) {
			top  += parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(body, "marginTop",  true) ) || 0;
			left += parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(body, "marginLeft", true) ) || 0;
		}

		return { top: top, left: left };
	},
	
	setOffset: function( elem, options, i ) {
		// set position first, in-case top/left are set even on static elem
		if ( /static/.test( jQuery.curCSS( elem, "position" ) ) ) {
			elem.style.position = "relative";
		}
		var curElem   = jQuery( elem ),
			curOffset = curElem.offset(),
			curTop    = parseInt( jQuery.curCSS( elem, "top",  true ), 10 ) || 0,
			curLeft   = parseInt( jQuery.curCSS( elem, "left", true ), 10 ) || 0;

		if ( jQuery.isFunction( options ) ) {
			options = options.call( elem, i, curOffset );
		}

		var props = {
			top:  (options.top  - curOffset.top)  + curTop,
			left: (options.left - curOffset.left) + curLeft
		};
		
		if ( "using" in options ) {
			options.using.call( elem, props );
		} else {
			curElem.css( props );
		}
	}
};


jQuery.fn.extend({
	position: function() {
		if ( !this[0] ) {
			return null;
		}

		var elem = this[0],

		// Get *real* offsetParent
		offsetParent = this.offsetParent(),

		// Get correct offsets
		offset       = this.offset(),
		parentOffset = /^body|html$/i.test(offsetParent[0].nodeName) ? { top: 0, left: 0 } : offsetParent.offset();

		// Subtract element margins
		// note: when an element has margin: auto the offsetLeft and marginLeft
		// are the same in Safari causing offset.left to incorrectly be 0
		offset.top  -= parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(elem, "marginTop",  true) ) || 0;
		offset.left -= parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(elem, "marginLeft", true) ) || 0;

		// Add offsetParent borders
		parentOffset.top  += parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(offsetParent[0], "borderTopWidth",  true) ) || 0;
		parentOffset.left += parseFloat( jQuery.curCSS(offsetParent[0], "borderLeftWidth", true) ) || 0;

		// Subtract the two offsets
		return {
			top:  offset.top  - parentOffset.top,
			left: offset.left - parentOffset.left
		};
	},

	offsetParent: function() {
		return this.map(function() {
			var offsetParent = this.offsetParent || document.body;
			while ( offsetParent && (!/^body|html$/i.test(offsetParent.nodeName) && jQuery.css(offsetParent, "position") === "static") ) {
				offsetParent = offsetParent.offsetParent;
			}
			return offsetParent;
		});
	}
});


// Create scrollLeft and scrollTop methods
jQuery.each( ["Left", "Top"], function( i, name ) {
	var method = "scroll" + name;

	jQuery.fn[ method ] = function(val) {
		var elem = this[0], win;
		
		if ( !elem ) {
			return null;
		}

		if ( val !== undefined ) {
			// Set the scroll offset
			return this.each(function() {
				win = getWindow( this );

				if ( win ) {
					win.scrollTo(
						!i ? val : jQuery(win).scrollLeft(),
						 i ? val : jQuery(win).scrollTop()
					);

				} else {
					this[ method ] = val;
				}
			});
		} else {
			win = getWindow( elem );

			// Return the scroll offset
			return win ? ("pageXOffset" in win) ? win[ i ? "pageYOffset" : "pageXOffset" ] :
				jQuery.support.boxModel && win.document.documentElement[ method ] ||
					win.document.body[ method ] :
				elem[ method ];
		}
	};
});

function getWindow( elem ) {
	return ("scrollTo" in elem && elem.document) ?
		elem :
		elem.nodeType === 9 ?
			elem.defaultView || elem.parentWindow :
			false;
}
// Create innerHeight, innerWidth, outerHeight and outerWidth methods
jQuery.each([ "Height", "Width" ], function( i, name ) {

	var type = name.toLowerCase();

	// innerHeight and innerWidth
	jQuery.fn["inner" + name] = function() {
		return this[0] ?
			jQuery.css( this[0], type, false, "padding" ) :
			null;
	};

	// outerHeight and outerWidth
	jQuery.fn["outer" + name] = function( margin ) {
		return this[0] ?
			jQuery.css( this[0], type, false, margin ? "margin" : "border" ) :
			null;
	};

	jQuery.fn[ type ] = function( size ) {
		// Get window width or height
		var elem = this[0];
		if ( !elem ) {
			return size == null ? null : this;
		}
		
		if ( jQuery.isFunction( size ) ) {
			return this.each(function( i ) {
				var self = jQuery( this );
				self[ type ]( size.call( this, i, self[ type ]() ) );
			});
		}

		return ("scrollTo" in elem && elem.document) ? // does it walk and quack like a window?
			// Everyone else use document.documentElement or document.body depending on Quirks vs Standards mode
			elem.document.compatMode === "CSS1Compat" && elem.document.documentElement[ "client" + name ] ||
			elem.document.body[ "client" + name ] :

			// Get document width or height
			(elem.nodeType === 9) ? // is it a document
				// Either scroll[Width/Height] or offset[Width/Height], whichever is greater
				Math.max(
					elem.documentElement["client" + name],
					elem.body["scroll" + name], elem.documentElement["scroll" + name],
					elem.body["offset" + name], elem.documentElement["offset" + name]
				) :

				// Get or set width or height on the element
				size === undefined ?
					// Get width or height on the element
					jQuery.css( elem, type ) :

					// Set the width or height on the element (default to pixels if value is unitless)
					this.css( type, typeof size === "string" ? size : size + "px" );
	};

});
// Expose jQuery to the global object
window.jQuery = window.$ = jQuery;

})(window);

/*
* 样式选择\xA8 颜色
*/
function tableSort(jqTableObj) {
    jqTableObj.find('thead th').click(
        function(){
            var dataType = $(this).attr('dataType');
            if(dataType == 'nosort'){return false;}
            var tableObj = $(this).closest('table');
            var index = tableObj.find('thead th').index(this) + 1;
            var arr = [];
            var row = tableObj.find('tbody tr');
            
            $.each(row, function(i){arr[i] = row[i]});
            
            if($(this).hasClass('current')){
                arr.reverse();
            } else {
                arr.sort(Utils.sortStr(index, dataType))
                
                tableObj.find('thead th').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
            }
            
            var fragment = document.createDocumentFragment();
            
            $.each(arr, function(i){
                fragment.appendChild(arr[i]);
            });
            
            tableObj.find('tbody').append(fragment);
        }
    );    
    
    var Utils = (function() {
        function sortStr(index, dataType){
            return function(a, b){
                var aText=$(a).find('td:nth-child(' + index + ')').attr('_order') || $(a).find('td:nth-child(' + index + ')').text();
                var bText=$(b).find('td:nth-child(' + index + ')').attr('_order') || $(b).find('td:nth-child(' + index + ')').text();
        
                if(dataType != 'text'){
                    aText=parseNonText(aText, dataType);
                    bText=parseNonText(bText, dataType);
                    
                    return aText > bText ? -1 : bText > aText ? 1 : 0;
                } else {
                    return aText.localeCompare(bText)
                }
            }
        }
        
        function parseNonText(data, dataType){
            switch(dataType){
                case 'int':
                    return parseInt(data) || 0
                case 'float':
                    return parseFloat(data) || 0
                default :
                return filterStr(data)
            }
        }
        
        //过滤中文字符\x8C$
        function filterStr(data){
            if (!data) {
                return 0;
            }
            
            return parseFloat(data.replace(/^[\\$a-zA-z\\u4e00-\\u9fa5 ]*(.*?)[a-zA-z\\u4e00-\\u9fa5 ]*$/,'$1'));
        }
        
        return {'sortStr' : sortStr};
    })();
}
/**
 * 随机\xB0
 */
function round(v, e) {
    var t = 1;
    for (; e > 0; t *= 10, e--)
        ;
    for (; e < 0; t /= 10, e++)
        ;
    return   Math.round(v * t) / t;
}
/**
 * 验证字符串长\xA6 支持中文
 * @param {type} str
 * @param {type} maxLen
 * @returns {Boolean}
 */
function checkLength(str, maxLen) {
    if (!str) {
        return false;
    }
    var iLength = 0;
    for (var i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
        if (str.charCodeAt(i) > 255) {
            iLength += 2;
        } else {
            iLength += 1;
        }
    }
    if (iLength > maxLen)
        return false;
    else
        return true;
}
/**
 * 过滤页面提交的数据中的HTML标签
 */
function htmlspecialchars(str)
{    
    str = str.replace(/&/g, '&amp;');
    str = str.replace(/</g, '&lt;');
    str = str.replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
    str = str.replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
    str = str.replace(/'/g, '&#039;');
    return str;  
}  
/**
 * 
 * @param {type} str
 * @param {type} 1 数字 2 英文 3 数字英文 4中文
 * @returns {@exp;str@call;replace}
 */
function isStrCheck(str, type) {
    if (type == 'undefined' || type == '' || type == 1) {
        return str.replace(/[^0-9.]+/ig, '');
    } else if (type == 2) {
        return str.replace(/[^a-z]+/ig, '');
    } else if (type == 3) {
        return str.replace(/[^0-9.a-z]+/ig, '');
    } else if (type == 4) {
        return str.replace(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g, '');
    }else{
        return str;
    }
}
String.prototype.len = function() {
    return this.replace(/[^\\x00-\\xff]/g, "**").length;
}
//Set maxlength for multiline TextBox
function setMaxLength(object, length)
{
    var result = true;
    //var controlid = document.selection.createRange().parentElement().id;
    //var controlValue = document.selection.createRange().text;
    var tempString = object.value;

    var tt = "";
    for (var i = 0; i < length; i++) {
        if (tt.len() < length)
            tt = tempString.substr(0, i + 1);
        else
            break;
    }
    if (tt.len() > length) {
        tt = tt.substr(0, tt.length - 1);
    }
    if (object.value.len() > length)
        object.value = tt;
}
/**
 * 手机号码验证
 * @param {type} str
 * @returns {Boolean}
 */

function isMobel(str) {
    if (!str) {
        return false;
    }
    if (str.length != 11)
        return false;
    var checked = /^1\\d{10}$/;
    if (checked.test(str)) {
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}
/**
 * 邮箱验证
 * @param {type} val
 * @returns {Boolean}
 */
function isEmail(val) {
    if (!val) {
        return false;
    }
    var checked = /^(\\w-*\\.*)+@(\\w-?)+(\\.\\w{2,})+$/;
    if (checked.test(val)) {
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}
/**
 * 是否为数\x97
 * @param {type} val
 * @returns {Boolean}
 */
function isIntval(val) {
    if (!val) {
        return false;
    }
    var checked = /^-?\\d+$/;
    if (checked.test(val)) {
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}

 * To change this license header, choose License Headers in Project Properties.
 * To change this template file, choose Tools | Templates
 * and open the template in the editor.
 */
function saveFile(fileurl) {
    if (typeof (openURLToBrowser) != "undefined") {
        openURLToBrowser(fileurl);
    } else
        window.open(fileurl);
}
//中文字符串截\x96
function zh_substr(str, len) {
    if (!str || !len) {
        return '';
    }
    //预期计数：中\x872字节，英\x871字节    
    var a = 0;      //循环计数    
    var i = 0;      //临时字串    
    var temp = '';
    for (i = 0; i < str.length; i++)
    {
        if (str.charCodeAt(i) > 255) {             //按照预期计数增加2           
            a += 2;
        } else {
            a++;
        }         //如果增加计数后长度大于限定长度，就直接返回临时字符串        
        if (a > len) {
            return temp;
        }          //将当前内容加到临时字符串        
        temp += str.charAt(i);
    }     //如果全部是单字节字符，就直接返回源字符串    
    return str;
}

// 遮罩\x82
function showDialog(divId) {
    var newDivId = createDivId(divId);
    var boarddiv = "<div id='" + newDivId + "' class='fullbg'></div> ";
    $("#" + divId).after(boarddiv);
	var popupName= $("#"+divId);
    var _scrollHeight = $(document).scrollTop(),//获取当前窗口距离页面顶部高度
	_windowHeight = $(window).height(),//获取当前窗口高度
	_windowWidth = $(window).width(),//获取当前窗口宽度
	_popupHeight = popupName.height(),//获取弹出层高\xA6
	_popupWeight = popupName.width();//获取弹出层宽\xA6
	_posiTop = (_windowHeight - _popupHeight)/2 + _scrollHeight;
	_posiLeft = (_windowWidth - _popupWeight)/2;
	popupName.css({"left": _posiLeft + "px","top":_posiTop + "px","display":"block"});//设置position	
    $("#" + divId).show();
}

function popup(popupName){
	var _scrollHeight = $(document).scrollTop(),//获取当前窗口距离页面顶部高度
	_windowHeight = $(window).height(),//获取当前窗口高度
	_windowWidth = $(window).width(),//获取当前窗口宽度
	_popupHeight = popupName.height(),//获取弹出层高\xA6
	_popupWeight = popupName.width();//获取弹出层宽\xA6
	_posiTop = (_windowHeight - _popupHeight)/2 + _scrollHeight;
	_posiLeft = (_windowWidth - _popupWeight)/2;
	popupName.css({"left": _posiLeft + "px","top":_posiTop + "px","display":"block"});//设置position
}

//关闭灰色 jQuery 遮罩
function hiddenDialog(divId) {
    var newDivId = createDivId(divId)
    $("#" + newDivId).remove();
    $("#" + divId).hide();
}

    html += '<div style="line-height:15px;float:left;margin-top:8px;margin-left:120px;" class="' + aclass + '">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>';
    html += '<div style="margin-left:5px;float:left;color:' + color + ';">' + message + '</div></div></div>'

    $("body").append(html);

}
/**
 * js 校验URl的合法\x80\xA7
 * @param {type} url
 * @returns {@exp;re@call;test|Boolean}
 */
function checkUrl(url) {
    if (!url) {
        return false;
    }
    //var strRegex = /^((https|http|ftp|rtsp|mms)?:\\/\\/)?(([0-9a-z_!~*'().&=+$%-]+: )?[0-9a-z_!~*'().&=+$%-]+@)?(([0-9]{1,3}\\.){3}[0-9]{1,4}|([0-9a-z_!~*'()-]+\\.)*([0-9a-z][0-9a-z-]{0,61})?[0-9a-z]\\.[a-z]{2,6})(:[0-9]{1,4})?((\\/?)|(\\/[0-9a-z_!~*'().;?:@&=+$,%#-]+)+\\/?)$/;
    //var strRegex = '(https?://)?((([a-z0-9\\\\-]+\\\\.)*?)([a-z0-9\\\\-]+(\\\\.(com|net|org|gov|cc|biz|info|cn|co|tv|in|me|top|asia)(\\\\.(cn|hk|uk|jp|tw))?)))([^\\\\s\\u4E00-\\u9FA5<]*)?([\\\\s\\u4E00-\\u9FA5<$]{1})';
    var strRegex = /((https|http|ftp|rtsp|mms)?:\\/\\/)?([\\w-]+\\.)+[\\w-]+(\\/[\\w- .\\/?%&=]*)?/;
    var re = new RegExp(strRegex);
    if (re.test(url)) {
        return true;
    } else {
        return false;
    }
}
/**
 * 文字 匹配 改变 颜色
 * @param {type} str
 * @param {type} value
 * @returns {String|@exp;str@call;replace}
 */
function replaces(str, value) {
    if (!str || !value) {
        return str;
    }
    return str.replace(value, '<span class=\\"highlight\\">' + value + '</span>');
}

function showTips(event,tips){
	var html = '<div style="max-width:400px;padding:10px; z-index:20000;word-wrap:break-word; display:none; word-break:break-all;text-align:left;background:#f8efb6;background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff, #e7e7f1);border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #767676;background:-webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0, #ffffff), color-stop(1, #e7e7f1));-webkit-box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676;-moz-box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676;box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676; position:absolute;"  id="divTips" name="divTips"></div>';
	$("body").append(html);
    x=event.clientX;  
    y=event.clientY;
    $('#divTips').html(tips);
    $('#divTips').css('left',x);  
    $('#divTips').css('top',y);  
    $('#divTips').show();
	
}

/**
 * 显示提示信息
 */
function titleShow(id, width) {
    var text = $("#" + id).attr('text_val');
    var html = '<div style="width:' + width + 'px; z-index:20000;word-wrap:break-word; word-break:break-all;text-align:left;background:#f8efb6;position:absolute;top:30px;line-height:25px;left:25%;background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff, #e7e7f1);border-radius:2px;border:1px solid #767676;background:-webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0, #ffffff), color-stop(1, #e7e7f1));text-indent:10px;-webkit-box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676;-moz-box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676;box-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #767676;"><div style="margin-left:3px;">' + text + '</div></div>';
    $("#" + id).after(html);
}

$(document).click(function(e) {
    $(document).find('[autohide=yes]').each(function() {
        if (e.target != this && !$.contains(this, e.target) && e.target != $(this).prev().get(0) && !$.contains($(this).prev().get(0), e.target)) {
            $(this).hide();
        }
    });
})
/**
 * 隐藏
 * @param {type} id
 * @returns {undefined}
 */
function HiddenSelect(id) {
    $('.' + id).hide();
}
/**
 *  中英文长度计\x97
 * @param {type} str
 * @returns {Number|@exp;str@pro;length|@exp;cArr@pro;length@exp;str@pro;length}
 */
function getStrLength(str) {
    var cArr = str.match(/[^\\x00-\\xff]/ig);
    return str.length + (cArr == null ? 0 : cArr.length);
}
/**
 * 单位时间内显示并隐藏
 * id 显示的地\xB9 #abc .adbc .aa
 * str 提示信息
 */
function hideTip(id, str) {
    $(id).show().html(str);
    setTimeout(function() {
        $(id).hide().html(''); //清空区块内容
    }, 2000);
}

//页内查找 18:18 2015/2/3
      $(function(){
        $('#search').keydown(function (e) {
            var key = e.which;
            if (key == 13) highlight();
        })
        var name = $('#search').attr('title'); 
        if(name=="account"){
            var cls = '.s_righ_cont';
            var sch = 'div[name="content"]';
        }else if(name=="webim"){
            var cls = '.grcyy';
            var sch = 'div[name="content"]';
        }else if(name=="consult"){
            var cls = '.table_s1';
            var sch = 'p[name="content"]';
        }
        var i = 0;
        var sCurText;
        function highlight(){
            clearSelection();//先清空一下上次高亮显示的内容\x9B             
            var flag = 0;
            var bStart = true;

            var searchText = $('#search').val();
            var _searchTop = $('#search').offset().top+30;
            var _searchLeft = $('#search').offset().left;
            if($.trim(searchText)==""){
                showTips("请输入查找的内容",_searchTop,3,_searchLeft);
                return;
            }
                 
            var searchText = $('#search').val();//获取你输入的关键字；
            var regExp = new RegExp(searchText, 'g');//创建正则表达式，g表示全局的，如果不用g，则查找到第\x80个就不会继续向下查找了；
            var content = $(cls).text();
            if (!regExp.test(content)) {
                showTips("没有找到要查找的名称",_searchTop,3,_searchLeft);
                return;
            } else {
                if (sCurText != searchText) {
                    i = 0;
                    sCurText = searchText;
                 }
             }
             
            $(sch).each(function(){
                var html = $(this).html();
                var newHtml = html.replace(regExp, '<span class="highlight">'+searchText+'</span>');//将找到的关键字替换，加上highlight属\x80；
                $(this).html(newHtml);//更新\x9B
            });
             
        }
        function clearSelection(){
            $(sch).each(function(){
                //找到\x80有highlight属\x80的元素\x9B
                $(this).find('.highlight').each(function(){
                    $(this).replaceWith($(this).html());//将他们的属\x80去掉；
                });
            });
        }
         
        //mask
        var tipsDiv = '<div class="tipsClass"></div>';
        $( 'body' ).append( tipsDiv );
        function showTips( tips, height, time,left ){
            var windowWidth = document.documentElement.clientWidth;
            $('.tipsClass').text(tips);
            $( 'div.tipsClass' ).css({
            'top' : height + 'px',
            'left' :left + 'px',
            'position' : 'absolute',
            'padding' : '8px 6px',
            'background': '#000000',
            'font-size' : 14 + 'px',
            'font-weight': 900,
            'margin' : '0 auto',
            'text-align': 'center',
            'width' : 'auto',
            'color' : '#fff',
            'z-index' : 20000,
            'border-radius':'2px',
            'opacity' : '0.8' ,
            'box-shadow':'0px 0px 10px #000',
            '-moz-box-shadow':'0px 0px 10px #000',
            '-webkit-box-shadow':'0px 0px 10px #000'
            }).show();
            setTimeout( function(){$( 'div.tipsClass' ).fadeOut();}, ( time * 1000 ) );
        }
      });

<div class="page_top"><span style="float: left;font-weight: bold;line-height: 24px;margin-left: 230px;">创建账户</span></div><script type="text/javascript">
    $(function() {
        var id = 'account';

        if (id == 'nodisp') {
            var arg = 'settingelse';
            if (arg != 'expression' && arg != 'personsetting' && arg != 'enterprise' && arg != 'robot' && arg != 'ticket' && arg != 'autoinvitation' && arg != 'platbinding' && arg != 'platformaccount' && arg != 'platformmt' && arg != 'platform') {
                arg = 'add_or_edit';
            }
            switch (arg) {
                case 'expression':
                    id = 'enterprise';
                    break;
                case 'personsetting':
                    id = 'personal';
                    break;
                case 'enterprise':
                    id = 'enterprise';
                    break;
                case 'platformaccount':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platformmt':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platbinding':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platform':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'account_management':
                    id = 'account';
                    break;
                case 'reception_group':
                    id = 'reception';
                    break;
                case 'key_pages':
                    id = 'keypage';
                    break;
                case 'black_list':
                    id = 'bklist';
                    break;
                case 'notice':
                    id = 'notice';
                    break;
                case 'autoinvitation':
                    id = 'reception';
                    break;
                case 'robot':
                    id = 'robot';
            }
            var url = location.href;
            window.location.href = url + '&disp=' + id;
        }
        $('#' + id).show();
        $('#' + id).prev().find('.icon_3_right').removeClass('icon_3_right').addClass('icon01');
        if (id != 'personal') {
            $('#personal').hide();
        }
    });
</script>

<script  type="text/javascript">


    $('.nav02').click(
            function() {
                var tip = $(this).next();
                if (tip.attr('class') == 's_left_m') {
                    $(this).next().toggle();
                    status = tip.css('display');
                    if (status == 'none') {
                        $(this).find('.icon_posi').removeClass('icon01').addClass('icon_3_right');
                    } else {
                        $(this).find('.icon_posi').removeClass('icon_3_right').addClass('icon01');
                    }
                }
            }
    );
    $('li').click(
            function() {
                window.location.href = $(this).children().attr('href');
            }
    );
</script>

function show_result(msg){
    if(msg=="1"){
        window.location.href = 'http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com/index.php/personsetting/index?userid=kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng&token=5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f&disp=personal';
    }else{
        $('#float_logo').show();
        $('#tip').html('保存失败');
    }    
}  
	function checkUserSubmit(){
		if(!onCheckSubmit('externalName',$.trim($('#externalName').val())))
			return;
		if(!onCheckSubmit('nickName',$.trim($('#nickName').val())))
			return;
		if($("#userForm input[name='usertype']").filter(':checked').val()==true){
			//是机器人
			if(!onCheckSubmit('no_reply',$('#no_reply').val()))
				return;
			if(!onCheckSubmit('welcome',$('#welcome').val()))
				return;
		}else{
			if(!onCheckSubmit('accountName',$.trim($('#accountName').val())))
				return;
			//不是机器人
			if(!onCheckSubmit('pass',$('#pass').val()))
				return;
			if(!onCheckSubmit('pass2',$('#pass2').val()))
				return;
			if($('#phoneservice')!=null && $('#phoneservice').val()=='1' && $('#phonepass')!=null && !onCheckSubmit('phonename',$.trim($('#phonename').val())))
				return;
			  
			if(!onCheckSubmit('hand_day_num',$.trim($('#hand_day_num').val())))
				return; 
			if(!onCheckSubmit('hand_all_num',$.trim($('#hand_all_num').val())))
				return;
														}
                var url = 'http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com/index.php/settingelse/add_account?userid=kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng&token=5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f';
        var postdata = $('#userForm').serialize()+'&accountName='+$('#accountName').val()+'&usericon='+$('#icon').attr("src");
        // console.log(postdata);
        // console.log(url);return;
		$.post(url,postdata,
            function(result){
				//console.log(result);
                if(result=='-4'){
                    $('#accountName_tip').atrr('class','f_red');
                    $('#accountName_tip').html('登录名不能为中文');
                }else if(result=='-1'){
                    $('#accountName_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#accountName_tip').html('该登录名已存在');
                }else if(result=='-3'){
                    $('#accountName_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#accountName_tip').html('您还没有登录，请登录');
                }else if(result=='-2'){
                    $('#accountName_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#accountName_tip').html('您没有添加用户的权限');
                }else if(result=='-5'){
                    $('#accountName_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#accountName_tip').html('用户数已达上限');
                }else if(result=='-6'){
                    $('#fenji_num_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#fenji_num_tip').html('分机号已经存在');
				}else if(result=='-8'){
                    $('#fenji_number_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#fenji_number_tip').html('分机号创建失败');
                }else if(result=='1'){
                    window.location.href="http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com/index.php/settingelse/account_management?userid=kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng&token=5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f&disp=account";
                }else{
                    $('#fenji_num_tip').attr('class','f_red');
                    $('#fenji_num_tip').html('创建分机号错误');
                }            
            
            }
        );
	}   
	function onCheckSubmit(type,val){
		var b=true;
		var msg='';
		var tipid='#'+type+'_tip';
		switch(type){
			case 'accountName':
				if($('#accountName').attr('disabled')==false){
					if(!val.length>0){
						b=false;
						msg='登录名不能为空';
					}else if(!checkLength(val,24)){
						b=false;
						msg='登录名不超过24个字符';
					}else{
						var regex=/^[0-9a-z_]{0,24}$/;
						if(!regex.test(val)){
							b=false;
							msg='登录名只能为小写英文、数字和下划线。';
						}
						var reg =/[\u4E00-\u9FA5\uFF00-\uFFFF]/g;
						if(reg.test(val)){
							b=false;
							msg='登录名不能含汉字';
						}
					}
				}
				break;
			case 'no_reply':
				if(!val.length>0){
					$("#no_reply").css("border","1px solid red");
					return false;
				}
				break;
			case 'welcome':
				if($('#robot_welcome').attr('style')!='display: none;'){
					if(!val.length>0){
						$("#welcome").css("border","1px solid red");
						return false;
					}
				}
				break;
			case 'nickName':
				if(!val.length>0){
					msg='内部名不能为空';
					b=false;
				}else if(!checkLength(val,32)){
					b=false;
					msg='内部名最多16个汉字或32个英文';
				}else{
					var regex=/^[a-zA-Z0-9_\u4e00-\u9fa5]+$/;
					if(!regex.test(val)){
						b=false;
						msg='只能为英文、数字、下划线和汉字。'
					}
				}
				break;
			case 'externalName':
				if(!val.length>0){
					msg='外部名不能为空';
					b=false;
				}else if(!checkLength(val,32)){
					b=false;
					msg='外部名最多16个汉字或32个英文';
				}else{
					var regex=/^[a-zA-Z0-9_\u4e00-\u9fa5]+$/;
                    
					if(!regex.test(val)){
						b=false;
						msg='只能为英文、数字、下划线和汉字。'
					}
				}
				break;
			case 'pass':
				if(val.length<6){
					b=false;
					msg='密码不少于6位';
				}else if(val.length>16){
					b=false;
					msg='密码不大于16位';
				}
				break;
			case 'pass2':
				if(val!=$('#pass').val()){
					b=false;
					msg='两次输入不一致';
				}
			case 'phonename':
				if(!val.length>0){
					msg='电话用户名不能为空';
					b=false;
				}
				break;
			case 'phonepass':
				if(!val.length>0){
					msg='电话密码不能为空';
					b=false;
				}
				break;
			case 'mobile':
				if(val.length>0){
					if(!/^0{0,1}(13[0-9]|15[0-9]|18[0-9])[0-9]{8}$/.test(val)){
						b=false;
						msg='请输入正确的手机号码';
					}
				}
				break;
			
      case 'hand_day_num':
      case 'hand_all_num':
        if(!verifyNum(val)){
          b=false;
          msg='请输入正确的数字(最大3位数)';
        }
        break;
      case 'fenji_num':
        if(val.length>0){
          if(!/^8\d{3}$/.test(val)){
            msg='请输入正确分机号码(必须是4位数且以8开头)';
            b=false;
          } 
        }
        break;
        case 'fenji_number':
			if(val.length>0){
				if(!/^[2-9]\d{3}$/.test(val)){
					msg='请输入正确分机号码(分机号取值范围1000-9999)';
					b=false;
				}
				var fenji_number = val;
								var url = 'http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com/index.php/settingelse/check_tinet_con?userid=kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng&token=5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f';
				if(fenji_number > 9999 || fenji_number < 1000){
					msg='请输入正确分机号码(分机号取值范围1000-9999)';
					b=false;
				}
				var postdata = 'con='+fenji_number;
				$.post(url,postdata,
					function(result){
						var Data = eval('(' + result + ')');
						if(Data.code == '1000'){
							msg='请输入正确分机号码(分机号已存在)';
							b=false;
						}
					});
			}
        break;
			default:
				break;
		}
		if(!b){
			$(tipid).attr('class','f_red');
			$(tipid).html(msg);
		}else{
			$(tipid).html(msg);
    }
		return b;
	}  
	function checkLength(str,maxLen){
		var iLength = 0;
		for(var i = 0;i<str.length;i++){
			if(str.charCodeAt(i) >255){
				iLength += 2;
			}else{
				iLength += 1;
			}
		}
		if(iLength>maxLen)
			return false;
		else
			return true;  
	}   
	$(function(){
		$('#account').attr('class','nav02 sele');
	}); 
	//定位显示tips
	function showTips(event,tips){  
		x=event.clientX;  
		y=event.clientY;  
		$('#divTips').html(tips);
		$('#divTips').css('left',x);  
		$('#divTips').css('top',y);  
		$('#divTips').show();;  
	}  
	function hiddenTips(){  
		document.getElementById("divTips").style.display="none";  
	}
	
	function verifyTinet(){
		var val = $("#fenji_number").val();
		if(val.trim() != ''){
			if(!/^[1-9]\d{3}$/.test(val)){
				console.log(val);
				msg='请输入正确分机号码(分机号取值范围1000-9999)';
				$("#fenji_number_tip").html('<span style="color:red">'+msg+'</span>');
				return;
			}
			var fenji_number = val;
						var url = 'http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com/index.php/settingelse/check_tinet_con?userid=kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng&token=5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f';
			if(fenji_number > 9999 || fenji_number < 1000){
				msg='请输入正确分机号码(分机号取值范围1000-9999)';
				$("#fenji_number_tip").html('<span style="color:red">'+msg+'</span>');
				return;
			}
			var postdata = 'con='+fenji_number;
			$.post(url,postdata,
				function(result){
					var Data = eval('(' + result + ')');
					if(Data.code == '1000'){
						msg='分机号已存在';
						$("#fenji_number_tip").html('<span style="color:red">'+msg+'</span>');
						return;
					}
			});
			
		}
	}
</script>

//编辑分组
function editGroup(gid,gname){
    var gname = encodeURIComponent(gname);
	
	//window.location.href = ROOTPATH+'/index.php/enterprise/edit_group_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token+'&gid=' + gid + "&gname=" + gname +'&disp=enterprise';

//删除分组
function delg(gid){
    var searchUrl = ROOTPATH+'/index.php/enterprise/delete_group_usage?userid='+ userid + '&token=' + token;
    var postdata = "delgid=" + gid;
    jQuery.post(searchUrl,postdata,
        function(data,status){
            if(status=='success'){
                if(data.result==1){
					window.location = ROOTPATH+'/index.php/enterprise/enterprise_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token+'&disp=enterprise';
                }else{
                    //删除分组失败
                    $('#pop').css('display','');
                    $('#pop').css('display','');
                    $('#pop .div_cont').html('删除分组失败');
                    $('#pop input[id="no"]').css('display','none');
                    delgid = -1;
                }                
            }
        }
    );
}
function cancelg(gid){
    $('#pop').css('display','none');
    delgid = -1;
}
function delGroup(gid){
	if(typeof(gid) == 'undefined') return;
	if(delgid == -1){
        $('#pop').css('display','');
        $('#yes').get(0).onclick=function(){delg(gid)}
        popup($("#pop"));
    }
}
//分组上移
function GroupUp(gid){
	var curObj = jQuery('#gr_'+gid);
	var upClass = curObj.attr('class');
	var _tmp,downClass;
    var tbid = curObj.prev().attr('id');
	//当前节点是否为第\x80个分\x84
    if(curObj.prev() && ('tableid' != tbid)){
	    _tmp = tbid.split('_');
	    upClass = jQuery('#gu_'+ _tmp[1]).attr('class');
    	SwapGroup(curObj.prev(),curObj);
    }else{
    	return;
    }
}
//交换分组位置
function SwapGroup(node1,node2){
	if(node1 && node2) {
		
		var tmp2 = node2.attr('id').split('_');
		var _tmp2 = tmp2[1];
		var tmp1 = node1.attr('id').split('_');
		var _tmp1 = tmp1[1];
		var tmp = jQuery('#grn_'+_tmp2).val();
		var _tmp = jQuery('#grn_'+_tmp1).val();
        
        var node1loc = node1.children('input').attr('loc');
        var node2loc = node2.children('input').attr('loc');        
        //排序,node1向下，node2向上
        if(node1loc=='none'&&node2loc=='last'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','last');
            node1.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(3)').children().children().removeClass('pos').addClass('posno');
           
            node2.children('input').attr('loc','none');
            node2.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(3)').children().children().removeClass('posno').addClass('pos');
        }else if(node1loc=='first'&&node2loc=='none'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','none');
            node1.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(4)').children().children().removeClass('pono').addClass('po');

            node2.children('input').attr('loc','first');
            node2.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(4)').children().children().removeClass('po').addClass('pono');
        }else if(node1loc=='first'&&node2loc=='last'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','last');
            node1.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(3)').children().children().removeClass('pos').addClass('posno');            
            node1.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(4)').children().children().removeClass('pono').addClass('po');

            node2.children('input').attr('loc','first');
            node2.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(3)').children().children().removeClass('posno').addClass('pos');
            node2.children('.grcyy_title').children().children(':nth-child(4)').children().children().removeClass('po').addClass('pono');
        }        
		jQuery('#grn_'+_tmp2).val(_tmp);
		jQuery('#grn_'+_tmp1).val(tmp);
        jQuery(node2).insertBefore(node1);
		GroupGrank(_tmp1,_tmp2,tmp,_tmp);
	}
}  
//交换分组数据库操\x9C
function GroupGrank(id1,id2,grank1,grank2){
    var searchUrl = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/group_grank?userid='+userid+'&token='+token;
    var postdata = "&id1=" + id1 + "&id2=" + id2 + "&grank1=" + grank1 + "&grank2=" + grank2;
    jQuery.post(searchUrl,postdata,
        function(data,status){
            if(status=='success'&& data.result==1){
                //alert(data.error);
                //window.location = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/enterprise_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token+'&disp=enterprise';
            }
        }
    );
}
//分组下移
function GroupDown(gid){
	var curObj = jQuery('#gr_'+gid);
    //当前节点是否为第\x80个分\x84
    var downClass = curObj.attr('class');
    //当前节点的后\x80条记录是否最后一条记\x95
    var _tmp,downClass;
    if(curObj.next()){
        _tmp = curObj.next().attr('id').split('_');
        downClass = jQuery('#gd_'+ _tmp[1]).attr('class');
    	SwapGroup(curObj,curObj.next());
    }else{
    	return;
    }
} 
//编辑常用\xAD
function editItem(cyytype,gid,id){
		if(cyytype=='create'){
			if(typeof(gid) == 'undefined') return;
			var postdata = '&gid='+ gid;
		}else{
			if(typeof(gid) == 'undefined' || typeof(id) == 'undefined') return;
			var response = jQuery("#fr_"+id).children('a').html();
			var rs = response.split('\x91');
			var title = rs[0].split('\x90')[1];
			if(typeof(title)=='undefined'){
				title = '';
				response = rs;
			}else{
				response = rs[1];
			}
			var postdata = '&gid='+ gid + '&id=' + id;
		}
        var searchUrl = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/edit_item_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token +postdata+'&disp=enterprise';
        //window.location = searchUrl;
		$.ajax({
			url: searchUrl,
			type: 'post',
			datatype: "html",
			data: null,
			success: function(data) {
				var data = eval('(' + data + ')');
				$("#edit_title").val(data.title);
				$("#edit_text").val(data.response);
				$("#option_html").html(data.option_html);
				$("#option_html").html(data.option_html);
				remLen.value = edit_text.value.length;
				addEvent(addInput);
				id_show("edit_tcc");
				if(cyytype=='create'){
					$("#usage_save").bind("click",function(){
						setGroup("create",gid);
					}); 
				}else{
					$("#usage_save").bind("click",function(){
						setGroup("save",data.id);
					}); 
				}
				

			}
		});
	
}
       
function addInput(e)
{
    var obj = e.target ? e.target : e.srcElement;
    var tags = document.getElementsByTagName('textarea');
    for(var i=0;i<tags.length;i++)
    {
        if(tags[i].getAttribute('url') == 'true'&&tags[i]!=obj)
        {
            tags[i].value = obj.value;
        }
    }
}
function addInput_input(e)
{
    var obj = e.target ? e.target : e.srcElement;
    var tags = document.getElementsByTagName('input');
    for(var i=0;i<tags.length;i++)
    {
        if(tags[i].getAttribute('url') == 'true'&&tags[i]!=obj)
        {
            tags[i].value = obj.value;
        }
    }
}
function addEvent(eventHandler)
    {
        var tags = document.getElementsByTagName('textarea');
        for(var i=0;i<tags.length;i++)
        {
            if(tags[i].getAttribute('url') == 'true')
            {
                if(tags[i].addEventListener)
                {
                    tags[i].addEventListener('keyup',eventHandler,true);
                }
                else
                {
                    tags[i].attachEvent('onkeyup',eventHandler);
                }
            }
        }
}
function addEvent_input(eventHandler)
    {
        var tags = document.getElementsByTagName('input');
        for(var i=0;i<tags.length;i++)
        {
            if(tags[i].getAttribute('url') == 'true')
            {
                if(tags[i].addEventListener)
                {
                    tags[i].addEventListener('keyup',eventHandler,true);
                }
                else
                {
                    tags[i].attachEvent('onkeyup',eventHandler);
                }
            }
        }
}
//删除常用\xAD
function delItem(id){
	if(typeof(id) == 'undefined') return;   
	var searchUrl = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/delete_item_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token;
	var postdata = {"delid": id};
    jQuery.post(searchUrl,postdata,
        function(data,status){
            if(data.result==1 && status=='success'){
                window.location = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/enterprise_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token+'&disp=enterprise';
            }else{
                //alert(data.error);
                $('#float_logo').show();
                $('#tip_err').html(data.error);                
            }
        }
    );
}
//上移分组常用\xAD
function MoveUp(id){
	if(typeof(id) == 'undefined') return;
    var curObj = jQuery('#msg_'+id);
    //当前节点是否为最后一条记\x95
    var tmp = curObj.attr('id').split('_');
    var downClass = jQuery('#md_'+ tmp[1]).attr('class');
    //当前节点是否为第\x80条记\x95
    var _tmp,upClass;
    if(curObj.attr('id')!=curObj.parent().children().first().attr('id')){
	    //当前节点的前\x80条记录是否为第一条记\x95
	    _tmp = curObj.prev().attr('id').split('_');
	    upClass = jQuery('#mu_'+ _tmp[1]).attr('class');
    	SwapNode(curObj.prev(),curObj);
    }else{
    	return;
    }
}
//下移分组常用\xAD
function MoveDown(id){
    if(typeof(id) == 'undefined') return;
    var curObj = jQuery('#msg_'+id);
	    //var curObj = obj.parentNode.parentNode;
	//当前节点是否为第\x80条记\x95
	var tmp = curObj.attr('id').split('_');
	var upClass = jQuery('#mu_'+ tmp[1]).attr('class');
	//当前节点的后\x80条记录是否最后一条记\x95
	var _tmp,downClass;
	if(curObj.attr('id')!=curObj.parent().children().last().attr('id')){
	    _tmp = curObj.next().attr('id').split('_');
	    downClass = jQuery('#md_'+ _tmp[1]).attr('class');
    	SwapNode(curObj,curObj.next());
	}else{
	   	return;
	}
}
//交换分组常用\xAD
function SwapNode(node1,node2){
	if(node1 && node2) {
		var tmp2 = node2.attr('id').split('_');
		var _tmp2 = tmp2[1];
		var tmp1 = node1.attr('id').split('_');
		var _tmp1 = tmp1[1];
		var tmp = jQuery('#gk_'+_tmp2).val();
        
        var node1loc = node1.children('input').attr('loc');
        var node2loc = node2.children('input').attr('loc');
        //排序,node1向下，node2向上
        if(node1loc=='none'&&node2loc=='last'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','last');
            node1.children('li').css('border','none');
            node1.children('li').children('.cnt_5').children().children().removeClass('pos').addClass('posno');
            node2.children('input').attr('loc','none');
            node2.children('li').css('border-bottom','1px dashed #d4d4d4');
            node2.children('li').children('.cnt_5').children().children().removeClass('posno').addClass('pos');            
        }else if(node1loc=='first'&&node2loc=='none'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','none');
            node1.children('li').children('.cnt_4').children().children().removeClass('pono').addClass('po');
            node2.children('input').attr('loc','first');
            node2.children('li').children('.cnt_4').children().children().removeClass('po').addClass('pono');
        }else if(node1loc=='first'&&node2loc=='last'){
            node1.children('input').attr('loc','last');
            node1.children('li').css('border','none');
            node1.children('li').children('.cnt_4').children().children().removeClass('pono').addClass('po');
            node1.children('li').children('.cnt_5').children().children().removeClass('pos').addClass('posno');
            node2.children('input').attr('loc','first');
            node2.children('li').css('border-bottom','1px dashed #d4d4d4');
            node2.children('li').children('.cnt_4').children().children().removeClass('po').addClass('pono');
            node2.children('li').children('.cnt_5').children().children().removeClass('posno').addClass('pos');            
        }        
		jQuery('#gk_'+_tmp2).val(jQuery('#gk_'+_tmp1).val());
		jQuery('#gk_'+_tmp1).val(tmp);
        jQuery(node2).insertBefore(node1);
		ChangeGrank(_tmp1,_tmp2,tmp,jQuery('#gk_'+_tmp2).val());
	}
}
//交换分组常用语排序编\xB7
function ChangeGrank(id1,id2,grank1,grank2){
	var searchUrl = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/change_grank?userid='+userid+'&token='+token;
	var postdata= {"id1" : id1, "id2": id2,"grank1": grank1, "grank2": grank2};
	
    jQuery.post(searchUrl,postdata,
        function(data,status){
            if(data.result==1 && status=='success'){
                //window.location = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/enterprise_usage?userid='+userid+'&token='+token + postdata+'&disp=enterprise';;
            }else{
                //alert(data.error);
                $('#float_logo').show();
                $('#tip_err').html(data.error);                 
            }
        }
    );
}
function htmlSpecical_decode(str){
    var temp = document.createElement("div");
    temp.innerHTML = str;
    var output = temp.innerText || temp.textContent;temp = null;
    return output;
}
//分组的展\x80与收\xA9
function icon_toggle(num,id,obj){
    var icon=$('#'+id).children('.grcyy_cont');
    icon.toggle();
    if(num==1){
        var handle = $(obj);
    }else{
        var handle = $(obj).prev().children();
    }
    var cls = handle.attr('class');
    if(cls=='icon_bot'){
        handle.removeClass('icon_bot').addClass('icon_right');
    }else{
       handle.removeClass('icon_right').addClass('icon_bot');
    }  
}
//定位显示tips
function showTips(event,tips){  
    x=event.clientX;  
    y=event.clientY;  
    $('#divTips').html(tips);
    $('#divTips').css('left',x);  
    $('#divTips').css('top',y);  
    $('#divTips').show();;  
}  
function hiddenTips(){
    document.getElementById("divTips").style.display="none";  
}
//弹出层居\xAD
function popup(popupName){
	var _scrollHeight = $(document).scrollTop(),//获取当前窗口距离页面顶部高度
	_windowHeight = $(window).height(),//获取当前窗口高度
	_windowWidth = $(window).width(),//获取当前窗口宽度
	_popupHeight = popupName.height(),//获取弹出层高\xA6
	_popupWeight = popupName.width();//获取弹出层宽\xA6
	_posiTop = (_windowHeight - _popupHeight)/2 + _scrollHeight-100;
	_posiLeft = (_windowWidth - _popupWeight)/2 -200;
	popupName.css({"left": _posiLeft + "px","top":_posiTop + "px","display":"block"});//设置position
}
/**
*	点击浏览相当于点击input:file
*/
function clickInputFile(){
	$('#scan').trigger('click');
}

/**
*	获取input:file文件名，并判断是否合法，目前只支\x81.csv文件
*/
function getFileName(){
	$('#filename').val('');
	var filename = $('#scan').val();
	if (filename.indexOf('.csv') > -1||filename.indexOf('.xls') > -1) {
		$('#filename').val(filename);
	} else {
		$('#scan').val('');
		$('#filename').val('非法文件类型\x81');
	}
}
/**
*	导入客户数据
*/
function loadCrm(){
	var url = ROOTPATH+'/index.php/enterprise/importUseful?userid='+userid+'&token='+token;
	var scan_val = $('#filename').val();
	if (scan_val == '') {
		
	} else if (scan_val == '非法文件类型\x81') {
		
	} else {
		$('#loadCsv').ajaxSubmit({
			url:url,
			type: 'POST',
			success: function(data) {
                if(data.result==1){
					//alert('上传成功');
					id_hide("daoru_tcc");
					$("#error_i").text(data.error_i);
					id_show("error_tcc");
				}else{
					//alert('上传失败');
					id_hide("daoru_tcc");
					$("#error_i").text(data.error_i);
					id_show("error_tcc");
				}
            }
		});
	}
}
function id_hide(id){
	$("#"+id).hide();
}
function id_show(id){
	$("#"+id).show();
}

//保存常用话术编辑
function setGroup(type,id) {
	//当前组id
    var curGid = $("#option_html").val();
	if (type == "save") {
		//当前常用话术id
		var curid = id;
		//\x80查常用话术名\xB0
		var tis = isLimititle();
		if(!tis) return;
		//内容
		if($.trim($('#edit_text').val())==''){
			$('#errmsg2').attr('class','f_red');
			$('#errmsg2').html('&nbsp;&nbsp;常用话术保存时不能为空\x80\x82');
			setTimeout(function(){$('#errmsg2').attr('class','f_gray');$('#errmsg2').html('&nbsp;&nbsp;不能超过500个汉\x97');},3000);  
			return;
		}
		var str = {'gid': curGid, 'id' : curid, 'type' : type};
		var msginfo = $.trim($('#edit_text').val());
		if(msginfo != ""){
			$.extend(str,{"response": encodeURIComponent(msginfo)});
			var tis = isLimititle2();
			if(!tis) return;            
		}
		var title = $.trim($("#edit_title").val());
		if(title){
			$.extend(str,{"title": encodeURIComponent('\x90'+title+'\x91')});		
		}
	} else {
		var tis = isLimititle();
		if(!tis) return;
		//内容
		if($.trim($('#edit_text').val())==''){
			$('#errmsg2').attr('class','f_red');
			$('#errmsg2').html('&nbsp;&nbsp;常用话术保存时不能为空\x80\x82');
			setTimeout(function(){$('#errmsg2').attr('class','f_gray');$('#errmsg2').html('&nbsp;&nbsp;不能超过500个汉\x97');},3000);  
			return;
		}
		var str = {'gid': curGid, 'type' : type};
		var msginfo = $.trim($('#edit_text').val());
		if(msginfo != ""){
			$.extend(str,{"response": encodeURIComponent(msginfo)});
			var tis = isLimititle2();
			if(!tis) return;            
		}
		var title = $.trim($("#edit_title").val());
		if(title){
			$.extend(str,{"title": encodeURIComponent('\x90'+title+'\x91')});		
		}
	}
	var searchUrl = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/edit_item_usage_save?userid=' + userid + '&token=' + token;
	var postdata = str;
		$.ajax({
			url: searchUrl,
			type: 'post',
			datatype: "html",
			data: postdata,
			success: function(data) {
				if (data.result == '1') {
					window.location = ROOTPATH + '/index.php/enterprise/enterprise_usage?userid=' + userid + '&token=' + token;
					id_hide("edit_tcc");
				}
			}
		});
}



//判断内容是否超过规定长度
    function isLimititle() {
		//组名字长度限\xB6
    var titleLength = 24;
        //处理群组名称
        var txt = $.trim($("#title").val());
        var len = getStrLength(txt) - (txt.split("\\n").length-1);          
        if (txt && len >titleLength) {
            $("#errmsg").attr('class','f_red');
            setTimeout(function(){$("#errmsg").attr('class','f_gray');},3000);
            return false;    
        }else{
            return true;
        }        
    }
//判断内容是否超过规定长度
    function isLimititle2() {
		//文字长度限制
    var limLength = 300;
        //处理群组名称
        var txt = $.trim($("#msginfo").val());
        var len = getStrLength(txt) - (txt.split("\\n").length-1);        
        if (txt && len >limLength) {
            $("#errmsg2").attr('class','f_red');
            setTimeout(function(){$("#errmsg2").attr('class','f_gray');},3000);
            return false;    
        }else{
            return true;
        }
    }
	function textCounter(field, countfield, maxlimit) {  
		 if (field.value.length > maxlimit){
			field.value = field.value.substring(0, maxlimit);  
		 }else{
			countfield.value = field.value.length; 
		 }
		 if(field.name=='no_reply'){
			$("#no_reply").css("border","1px solid #d4d4d4");
		 }
		 if(field.name=='welcome'){
			$("#welcome").css("border","1px solid #d4d4d4");
		 }
	}
	function textCounter_input(field, countfield, maxlimit) {
		 if ($("#"+field).val().length > maxlimit){  
		  $('#'+field).attr("value",$('#'+field).val().substring(0, maxlimit));
		 }else{  
			$('#'+countfield).attr("value",$('#'+field).val().length);
		 }
	}
	function logo_upload(){
    $('#info').css('display','');
}

    $('#input_div_list').toggle();
    $('#input_div_list2').hide();

    $('#input_div_list').hide();
    $('#input_div_list3').hide();
    $('#div_deal').hide();    
}

    $('#input_div_list').hide();
    $('#div_deal').hide();
}
function liuyan(){
    if($('#current_pri').html()=="管理\x98"){
        $('#current_deal').html('全部');
        return;
    }    
    $('#div_deal').toggle();
    $('#input_div_list3').hide();
    $('#input_div_list2').hide();
    $('#input_div_list').hide();
}
function is_robot(type){
	if(type==0){
		$(".robot_class").show();
		$(".robot_icon").hide();
	}else{
		$('#remLen').attr("value",$('#no_reply').val().length);
		$('#remLen1').attr("value",$('#welcome').val().length);
		if($("#userForm input[name='is_robot_welcome']").filter(':checked').val()==true){
			$("#robot_welcome").show();
		}else{
			$("#robot_welcome").hide();
		}
		$(".robot_class").hide();
		$(".robot_icon").show();
	}
}
function choosePri(role){
		$('#pri').val(role);
		var pri_arr=new Array();
		pri_arr['admin']='管理\x98';
		pri_arr['inspector']='质检\x98';
		pri_arr['sale']='\x80\xAE';
		pri_arr['groupleader']='组长';
		$('#current_pri').html(pri_arr[role]);
		$('#input_div_list').hide();
        $('#current_deal').html('全部');
		if(role=='admin'){
			$('#dealkfid').val('all');
			$('#deal_tip').html('&nbsp;管理员可以查看所有的留言');
            $('#current_deal').get(0).onclick=function(){return false;}
		}else{
			$('#dealkfid').val('all');
			$('#deal_tip').html('&nbsp;请\x80择留言\x80属客服的分组');
            $('#current_deal').get(0).onclick=function(){liuyan();}
		}
	}
	function chooseGroup(k,groupname){
		$('#current_group').html(groupname);
		$('#current_group').get(0).onmouseover=function(event){showTips(event,groupname);};
		$('#gid').val(k);
	}
	function checkChi(target,e){
        e=window.event||e;
        if(e.keyCode == 46 || e.keyCode == 8 || e.keyCode == 35 || e.keyCode == 36 || (e.keyCode >= 37 && e.keyCode <= 40)){
			return;
        }
        if(/[^x00-xff]/.test(target.value))
            target.value=target.value.replace(/[\\u4E00-\\u9FA5\\uFF00-\\uFFFF]/g, '');
    }
	function d(type){
		var tipid='#'+type+'_tip';
		$(tipid).attr('class','');
		switch(type){
			case "accountName":
				if($('#accountName').attr('disabled')==false){
					$(tipid).html('不能为中文，\x80\x9A24个字\xA6');
				}
				break;
			case "nickName":
				$(tipid).html('\x80\x9A16个汉\x97');
				break;
			case "externalName":
				$(tipid).html('\x80\x9A16个汉\x97');
				break;
			case "pass":
				$(tipid).html('\xB16-20个英文字\x8D/数字或特殊字符组\x90');
				break;
			case "pass2":
				$(tipid).html('请再次输入密\x81');
				break;
			case "phonename":
				$(tipid).html('请输入电话用户名');
				break;
			case "phonepass":
				$(tipid).html('请输入电话用户密\x81');
				break;
			case "mobile":
				$(tipid).html('请输入接收留\x80通知的手机号\x81');
				break;
			case "email":
				$(tipid).html('请输入接收留\x80通知的Email地址');
				break;
			case "hand_day_num":
          $(tipid).html('请输入每日新增上限数\x8F');
      break;
      case "hand_all_num":
          $(tipid).html('请输入工单\x80上限数\x8F');
          break;
      case "fenji_num":
          $(tipid).html('请输入分机号\x81(必须\xAF4位数且以8\x80\xB4)');
          break;
      default:
				break;
		}
	}
	function verifyNum(val){
		var reg = /^\\d{1,3}$/;
		if(!reg.exec(val)){
			return false;
		}else{
			return true;
		}
	}
	function chooseDeal(id,name){
		$('#current_deal').html(name);
		$('#dealkfid').val(id);
		$('#div_deal').css('display','none');
        if($('#current_pri').html()=="管理\x98"){
            $('#current_deal').html('全部');
            $('#div_deal').css('display','none');
        }        
	}
	function chooseRep(num){
		$('#maxreception').val(num);
		$('#current_rep').html(num);
	} 
	function checkLength(str,maxLen){
		var iLength = 0;
		for(var i = 0;i<str.length;i++){
			if(str.charCodeAt(i) >255){
				iLength += 2;
			}else{
				iLength += 1;
			}
		}
		if(iLength>maxLen)
			return false;
		else
			return true;  
	}

	function showTips(event,tips){  
		x=event.clientX;  
		y=event.clientY;  
		$('#divTips').html(tips);
		$('#divTips').css('left',x);  
		$('#divTips').css('top',y);  
		$('#divTips').show();;  
	}

		document.getElementById("divTips").style.display="none";  
	}

function useCamera()
		{
			var content = '<embed height="464" width="514" ';
			content +='flashvars="type=camera';
			content +='&postUrl='+cameraPostUrl+'?&radom=1';
			content += '&saveUrl='+saveUrl+'?radom=1" ';
			content +='pluginspage="http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" ';
			content +='allowscriptaccess="always" wmode="transparent" quality="high" ';
			content +='src="'+editorFlaPath+'"/>';
			document.getElementById('avatar_editor').innerHTML = content;
		}
		function buildAvatarEditor(pic_id,pic_path,post_type)
		{   
			var content = '<embed height="464" width="514"'; 
			content+='flashvars="type='+post_type;
			content+='&photoUrl='+pic_path;
			content+='&photoId='+pic_id;
			content+='&postUrl='+cameraPostUrl+'?radom=1';
			content+='&saveUrl='+saveUrl+'?radom=1&test=100"';
			content+=' pluginspage="http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer"';
			content+=' type="application/x-shockwave-flash"';
			content+=' allowscriptaccess="always" wmode="transparent" quality="high" src="'+editorFlaPath+'"/>';
			document.getElementById('avatar_editor').innerHTML = content;
		}
			/**
			  * 提供给FLASH的接\xA3 \x9A 没有摄像头时的回调方\x95
			  */
			 function noCamera(){
                $('#float_logo').show();
                $('#tip').html('没有摄像\xB4');                  
			 }
					
			/**
			 * 提供给FLASH的接口：编辑头像保存成功后的回调方法
			 */
			function avatarSaved(msg){
                var obj=$.parseJSON(msg); 
                overupload(obj.url);
				$('#msg').fadeIn(1000);
				$('#info').fadeOut(1000);
			}
			
			 /**
			  * 提供给FLASH的接口：编辑头像保存失败的回调方\x95, msg 是失败信息，可以不返回给用户, 仅作调试使用.
			  */
			 function avatarError(msg){
                $('#float_logo').show();
                $('#tip').html('上传失败\x86');                  
				//alert("上传失败\x86");
			 }
			var selectVideo = false;
				function uploadVideo()
				{
					var uuid=1;
					
					var som = new SWFObject(baseurl + '/up/swf/up.swf', 'uploader_video', '84', '25', '8', '');
					som.addParam('allowScriptAccess', 'always');
					som.addParam('FlashVars',"t=3&m=0&s=10240000&n=UploadVideo&c=1&uuid="+1); //参数t表示允许上传的文件类\x8B0：所有文\xB6,1：视频文\xB6,2：mp3,3:图片
					som.addParam('wmode','transparent');
					som.write('upload_flash_video');
				}

				var UploadVideo = {
				isUploading:false,
				onSelect:function(args){
					
					//选择视频文件
					if (args[0].status == 1){
						selectVideo = true;
						$('#uploadp').html(args[0].name);
						$('#type').val(args[0].type);
					} 
					if (args[0].status == '-1') {
                        $('#float_logo').show();
                        $('#tip').html('文件超过\x80大尺\xB8');                         
                        //alert('文件超过\x80大尺\xB8');
					}
					UploadVideo.submit(); //自动上传
				},
				onProgress:function(args){
					//正在进行文件上传
					var width=parseInt((args.bytesLoaded/args.bytesTotal)*236)+'px';
					$('#e').css("width", width);
					$('#e').html(parseInt((args.bytesLoaded/args.bytesTotal)*100)+"%");
					$('#filesize').html((args.bytesLoaded/1024).float_n(2)+'KB/'+(args.bytesTotal/1024).float_n(2)+'KB');
				},
				onComplete:function(args){
					//文件上传成功
					if(args)
					{
						if(args.status=='1'){
							eval(args.data); //获取服务端返回的数据
							//$('#ex').html(args.data);
							$('#fsize').val($('#filesize').html());
                            //$('#float_logo').show();
                            //$('#tip').html('文件上传成功');                            
							//alert('文件上传成功');
							this.isUploading = false;
							return true;
						}
						if(args.status=='-4') {
                            $('#float_logo').show();
                            $('#tip').html('IO错误');
						//alert('IO错误');
						return false;
						}
						if(args.status=='2') {
                            $('#float_logo').show();
                            $('#tip').html('空间不足');                            
                            //alert('空间不足');
						return false;
						}
						if(args.status=='3') {
                            $('#float_logo').show();
                            $('#tip').html('安全错误');
                            //alert('安全错误\x82');
						return false;
						}
                        $('#float_logo').show();
                        $('#tip').html('对不\xB7,服务器忙,请稍后重\x95.');                        
						//alert('对不\xB7,服务器忙,请稍后重\x95.');
						return false;
					}else{
                        $('#float_logo').show();
                        $('#tip').html('对不\xB7,服务器忙,请稍后重\x95.');
                        //alert('对不\xB7,服务器忙,请稍后重\x95.');
						return false;
					}
				},
				onAllComplete:function(args){
				//批量上传时，\x80有文件上传完\x90
				},
				onAllRemove:function(args){
				//\x80有文件都移除

    $(function() {
        var id = 'account';

        if (id == 'nodisp') {
            var arg = 'settingelse';
            if (arg != 'expression' && arg != 'personsetting' && arg != 'enterprise' && arg != 'robot' && arg != 'ticket' && arg != 'autoinvitation' && arg != 'platbinding' && arg != 'platformaccount' && arg != 'platformmt' && arg != 'platform') {
                arg = 'account_management';
            }
            switch (arg) {
                case 'expression':
                    id = 'enterprise';
                    break;
                case 'personsetting':
                    id = 'personal';
                    break;
                case 'enterprise':
                    id = 'enterprise';
                    break;
                case 'platformaccount':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platformmt':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platbinding':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'platform':
                    id = 'platform';
                    break;
                case 'account_management':
                    id = 'account';
                    break;
                case 'reception_group':
                    id = 'reception';
                    break;
                case 'key_pages':
                    id = 'keypage';
                    break;
                case 'black_list':
                    id = 'bklist';
                    break;
                case 'notice':
                    id = 'notice';
                    break;
                case 'autoinvitation':
                    id = 'reception';
                    break;
                case 'robot':
                    id = 'robot';
            }
            var url = location.href;
            window.location.href = url + '&disp=' + id;
        }
        $('#' + id).show();
        $('#' + id).prev().find('.icon_3_right').removeClass('icon_3_right').addClass('icon01');
        if (id != 'personal') {
            $('#personal').hide();
        }
    });
</script>
