<script  type="text/javascript">


    $('.nav02').click(
            function() {
                var tip = $(this).next();
                if (tip.attr('class') == 's_left_m') {
                    $(this).next().toggle();
                    status = tip.css('display');
                    if (status == 'none') {
                        $(this).find('.icon_posi').removeClass('icon01').addClass('icon_3_right');
                    } else {
                        $(this).find('.icon_posi').removeClass('icon_3_right').addClass('icon01');
                    }
                }
            }
    );
    $('li').click(
            function() {
                window.location.href = $(this).children().attr('href');
            }
    );
</script>
<script>
	function groupHide(obj){
		var tobj=$(obj).parent().parent().next().find('.zhgl_table2');
		if($(obj).attr('className')=='div_down'){
			tobj.css('display','none');
			$(obj).attr('className','div_up');
		}else if($(obj).attr('className')=='div_up'){
			tobj.css('display','');
			$(obj).attr('className','div_down');
		}
	}
	
	function searchName(){
		var searched=$('.input_zhgl').val().trim();
		var thisName='';
		var txt='';
		if(searched=='查找帐户' || searched==''){
			$('#search_div').empty();
			$('#search_div').css('display','none');
			$('td[name=td_name]').css('color','#757E79');
			$('td[name=td_nickname]').css('color','#757E79');
			return;
		}
		var all_tds=$('td[name=td_name]');
		var all_ready_match=0;
		if(all_tds.length>0){
			for(var i=0,len=all_tds.length;i<len;i++){
				if(all_ready_match>=20)
					break;
				thisName=all_tds.eq(i).html();
				thisName=thisName+'----'+all_tds.eq(i).next().html();
				if(thisName.indexOf(searched)!=-1){
					txt+="<div onclick='locateName("+i+","+all_tds.eq(i).attr('user_id')+");$(\".input_zhgl\").val(\""+thisName+"\")'>"+thisName+"</div>";
					all_ready_match++;
				}
			}
		}
		$('#search_div').empty();
		$('#search_div').append(txt);
		$('#search_div').css('display','block');
	}
	function locateName(i,user_id){
		$('.div_up').each(function(){groupHide(this);});
		$('td[name=td_name]').css('color','#757E79');
		$('td[name=td_nickname]').css('color','#757E79');
		var jobj=$('td[name=td_name]').eq(i);
		jobj.css('color','#FF0000');
		jobj.next().css('color','#FF0000');
		$('#search_div').css('display','none');
		location.href='#tr_'+user_id;

	}
//--------10:13 2014/11/11---------
var ROOTPATH = 'http://kpi3-test.ntalker.com';
var usrid = 'kf_1111_ISME9754_T2D_ntalker_lizhipeng';
var token = '5a0b1a6d6215136d4d415d4d8cef378f';

	function showEditGroup(gid,gname){
		$('#addoredit_title').html('编辑分组');
		$('#groupname').val(gname);
		$('#editOrAddGroup').val('2');
		$('#editid').val(gid);
		$('#div_addgroup').css('display','block');
	}
	function showAddGroup(){
		$('#addoredit_title').html('新建分组');
		$('#editOrAddGroup').val('1');
		$('#div_addgroup').css('display','block');
        popup($("#div_addgroup"));
        
	}
	function addOrEditGroup(siteid,userid,token){
		var groupname=$.trim($('#groupname').val());
		if(groupname.length>16){
            $('#float_logo').show();
            $('#tip_err').html('分组名称不能超过16个字');            
			return;
		}
		var flag=$('#editOrAddGroup').val();
		groupname=encodeURIComponent(groupname);
		if(flag=='1'){
			var url=ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/add_group?userid='+userid+"&token="+token;
            var postdata={"groupname":groupname};
		}else if(flag=='2'){
			var gid=$('#editid').val();
			var url=ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/edit_group?userid='+userid+"&token="+token+"&groupname="+groupname+"&gid="+gid;
		}
		$.post(url,postdata,
            function(result){
                	if(result=='1'){
                		window.location.reload();
                	}
                }
        );
	}
	function delGroup(gid,siteid,userid,token,act){
		if(act=='check'){
			var url=ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/del_group?userid='+userid+"&token="+token;
            var postdata={"act":'check',"gid":gid};
			$.post(url,postdata,
                function(result){
                	if(result=='-1'){
                		$('#del_msg').html('提示');
                		$('#div_can .div_cont').html('请您先删除该组下面的所有成员。');
						$('#delButton').val('关闭');
						$('#button_cancle').css('display','none');
						$('#delButton').get(0).onclick=function(){ $('#div_can').css('display','none') };
						$('#div_can').css('display','block');
                	}else if(result=='1'){
						$('#del_msg').html('提示');
						$('#div_can .div_cont').html('您确认要删除该组?');
						$('#delButton').val('确定');
						$('#delButton').get(0).onclick=function(){delGroup(gid,siteid,userid,token,'do')};
						$('#div_can').css('display','block');
					}
                    popup($("#div_can"));
				}
        	);
		}else if(act=='do'){
			var url=ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/del_group?userid='+userid+"&token="+token;
            var postdata={"act":'do',"gid":gid};
            $.post(url,postdata,
                function(result){
                	if(result=='1'){
                		location.reload();
					}
				}
        	);
		}
		return;
	} 
	function deleteUser(userid,adminid,siteid){
	    $('#del_msg').html('提示');
	    $('.div_cont').html('您确认要删除该用户?');
		$('#button_cancle').css('display','');
		$('#delButton').val('确定');
		$('#delButton').get(0).onclick=function(){delUser(userid,adminid,siteid)};
		$('#div_can').css('display','block');
	} 
	function delUser(userid,adminid,siteid){
		var url=ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/del_account?token='+token+"&userid="+adminid;
        var postdata = {'uid':userid};
        $.post(url,postdata,
            function(data){
                if(data==1){
                    $('#div_can').hide();
                    window.location.reload();
                }
            
            }
        );
	} 
	function show_active(id,userid){
		$('#div_can2').css('display','block');
		$('#active_button').get(0).onclick=function(){setActive(id,userid)};
        popup($("#div_can2"));
	}
	function setActive(id,userid){
	    $.ajax({
                url:ROOTPATH+'/index.php/settingelse/set_active?id='+id+"&userid="+userid,
                type:'GET',
                datatype:"html",
                data:null,
                beforeSend:function(){ 
                					$('#div_can2').css('display','none'); 
                					},
                success:function(result){
                	if(result!='-3' && result!='-2' && result!='-1'){
                		var insert=$('#span_'+id).html();
						if(insert=='禁用'){
							$('#span_'+id).html('启用');
                            window.location.reload();
						}else if(insert=='启用'){
							$('#span_'+id).html('禁用');
                            window.location.reload();
						}
                	}
                }
        });
	} 
//弹出层居中
function popup(popupName){
	var _scrollHeight = $(document).scrollTop(),//获取当前窗口距离页面顶部高度
	_windowHeight = $(window).height(),//获取当前窗口高度
	_windowWidth = $(window).width(),//获取当前窗口宽度
	_popupHeight = popupName.height(),//获取弹出层高度
	_popupWeight = popupName.width();//获取弹出层宽度
	_posiTop = (_windowHeight - _popupHeight)/2 + _scrollHeight;
	_posiLeft = (_windowWidth - _popupWeight)/2;
	popupName.css({"left": _posiLeft + "px","top":_posiTop + "px","display":"block"});//设置position
}    
</script>
